itics and history.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aRight and left (Political science)zEnglandzSheffieldxHistoryy20th century. 0aSocialismzEnglandzSheffieldxHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Great Britain / 20th Century.2bisacsh  aActivism.  aIdentity politics.  aLabour Party.  aLabour movement.  aLocal government.  aNew social movements.  aSheffield.  aSingle issue politics.  aSocial democracy.  aSouth Yorkshire.1 aPayling, Daisy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978152615031840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526150318423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526150318/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles